<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Form_Element_Select supports option groups, but the default validator (InArray) is not given the correct values to test for.</p>

&lt;?php

$form = new Zend_Form();
$form-&gt;setMethod('post');
$form-&gt;addElement($form-&gt;createElement('select', 'profession')
    -&gt;setLabel('Profession')
    -&gt;setMultiOptions(array(
        'Technology' =&gt; array(
            '1'     =&gt; 'Web Developer',
            '2'     =&gt; 'Software Engineer'
        )
    ))
);
$form-&gt;addElement($form-&gt;createElement('submit', 'submit')
    -&gt;setLabel("Submit")
);

$fakePostData = array('profession' =&gt; '1');

$form-&gt;isValid($fakePostData);  // Not valid

?&gt;

